e=\"line-height: 23px;\">第五名内蒙古队</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 23px;\">男子</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 23px;\">第一名山东队</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 23px;\">第二名解放军队</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 23px;\">第三名上海队</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 23px;\">第四名北京队</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 23px;\">第五名内蒙古队</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:18px;\"><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070102256672.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070102442885.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070103045446.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070103521265.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070104105276.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070104252429.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070104427143.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070104597404.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070105152199.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070105305853.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070105484286.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070106041117.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070106222634.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070106394672.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070106567372.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070107128623.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070107293452.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/07/201411070107477825.JPG\" width=\"700\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>',1),(67,8,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">     阿迪达斯公布了与11月5日迄今为止科技含量最高的最新全黑战袍。<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    全黑将在他们北半球之旅的第二场比赛，也就是在Twickenham与英格兰队较量是披上新战袍。<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    新式的全黑战袍是阿迪达斯公司历时两年，在全黑老<span style=\"line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">球员Richie McCaw，Dan Carter，Liam Messam，Aaron Smith，Israel Dagg和Conrad Smith的配合之下设计完成的。因为球员穿着合适是橄榄球球衣设计最重要的一个方面。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    阿迪达斯使用了称为“动态伸展分析”的通常应用于航天的突破性技术，该技术可以测量出球员运动时皮肤会受多大的力。在此基础上阿迪达斯，仿生球员的皮肤，针对前锋和后锋分别设计了两款球衣。因为前锋在Scrum中需要抓住衣服，而后锋则需要紧身以防被抓住，所以针对前后锋有不同的设计实在是太棒了。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    新战袍的织物技术具有可以双向拉伸的特点。阿迪达斯团队通过过对碳纤维织物的开发，可以保证抗拉扯，又柔韧，既轻又舒服，确保可以经受比赛的严峻考验。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    Carters说，新球衣不仅是采用了最新进的技术，更是他所穿过的最舒服的球衣，“简直就像是自己的第二层衣服”。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">想买球衣的球迷可以有三个选择：<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    120美元的支持者棉质球衣，不过只限新西兰；</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    150美元的Climacool版球衣；</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    200美元的顶级比赛版球衣。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    无图无真相，心动了么？来一件吧，嘿嘿。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148069259.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148312217.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148319687.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148326714.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148324578.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148325921.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148331335.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080147211357.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080147292640.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080147395312.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /></p>',1),(68,8,'<p><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080149288127.jpg\" width=\"500\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080149406162.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p><p></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    全黑能在橄榄球的老家英格兰拿下这次胜利么？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    如果他们能，这将是他们的第400次国际正式比赛（Test）的胜利（524场比赛里）！</p><br /><p><br /></p>',1),(70,8,'<p><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/10/201411100019123520.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p><p>这两天进行了太多的比赛，爱尔兰在都柏林击败南半球来的巨人南非。还有新西兰艰难战胜英格兰，澳大利亚连续第十次击败威尔士。</p><p>橄榄球测试赛周末比分速览：</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12px; color: rgb（51, 51, 51）; font-family: Verdana; line-height: 18px; text-align: justify;\">日本 18 -&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px; color: rgb（51, 51, 51）; font-family: Verdana; line-height: 18px; margin: 0px; list-style-type: none;\"><strong>20 毛利全黑</strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; list-style-type: none; text-align: justify; line-height: 18px; color: rgb（51, 51, 51）; font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; list-style-type: none;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; list-style-type: none;\"><strong>加拿大 17</strong></span>&nbsp;- 13 纳米比亚</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; list-style-type: none; text-align: justify; line-height: 18px; color: rgb（51, 51, 51）; font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; list-style-type: none;font-size:12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; list-style-type: none; text-align: justify; line-height: 18px; color: rgb（51, 51, 51）; font-family: Verdana;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; list-style-type: none;font-size:12px;\">英格兰 21 -&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; list-style-type: none;\"><strong>24 新西兰</strong></span></span></p><p st