le=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px 4px; border: 0px; color: rgb（95, 95, 95）; font-family: 宋体, ‘Lucida Grande‘, Verdana, Lucida, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, arial; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;\">　　今年18岁的王婷婷是中国队的主力球员，在铜牌争夺战中也是首发出场。王婷婷5年前开始在城阳体育训练基地接受专业的橄榄球训练，是中国队12名球员中 “球龄”最长的。相比绝大多数半路出家的队友，王婷婷可谓科班出身，她练习的首个项目便是橄榄球。对于女孩子来说，对抗异常激烈的橄榄球运动非常艰苦，虽然由于经常倒地，王婷婷的胳膊上伤痕累累，但她却无怨无悔，“这枚沉甸甸的铜牌，更加坚定了我从事这项运动的决心和信念，希望有朝一日在奥运赛场上取得佳绩。”</p>',0),(17,7,1,1,'默认管理员','魅力橄榄球——2014全国青年七人制橄榄球锦标赛图锦','七人制橄榄球','',1,'',1409206634,'','',0,50,'',1409206634,0,'<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416351590.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416357263.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416351431.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416351184.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416362339.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416366235.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416367866.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416364722.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416367886.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/08/28/201408281416375030.jpg\" alt=\"\" />',0),(18,14,1,1,'默认管理员','女子橄榄球赛','橄榄球','',1,'',1409816196,'','27/73/494582af43d9',0,102,'',1409793950,0,'<embed src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNzcyNDA5MDA4/v.swf\" allowFullScreen=\"true\" quality=\"high\" width=\"1100\" height=\"600\" align=\"middle\" allowScriptAccess=\"always\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\"></embed>',0),