cCaw，Dan Carter，Liam Messam，Aaron Smith，Israel Dagg和Conrad Smith的配合之下设计完成的。因为球员穿着合适是橄榄球球衣设计最重要的一个方面。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    阿迪达斯使用了称为“动态伸展分析”的通常应用于航天的突破性技术，该技术可以测量出球员运动时皮肤会受多大的力。在此基础上阿迪达斯，仿生球员的皮肤，针对前锋和后锋分别设计了两款球衣。因为前锋在Scrum中需要抓住衣服，而后锋则需要紧身以防被抓住，所以针对前后锋有不同的设计实在是太棒了。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    新战袍的织物技术具有可以双向拉伸的特点。阿迪达斯团队通过过对碳纤维织物的开发，可以保证抗拉扯，又柔韧，既轻又舒服，确保可以经受比赛的严峻考验。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    Carters说，新球衣不仅是采用了最新进的技术，更是他所穿过的最舒服的球衣，“简直就像是自己的第二层衣服”。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">想买球衣的球迷可以有三个选择：<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    120美元的支持者棉质球衣，不过只限新西兰；</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    150美元的Climacool版球衣；</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    200美元的顶级比赛版球衣。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">    无图无真相，心动了么？来一件吧，嘿嘿。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148069259.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb（62, 62, 62）; font-family: ‘Helvetica Neue‘, Helvetica, ‘Hiragino Sans GB‘, ‘Microsoft YaHei‘, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"http://public.51rugby.com/uploadfiles/article/2014/11/08/201411080148312217.